+# Coordination Log
+
+Use this file to share decisions, status updates, and context with other agents.
+Write your updates below. There is no enforced format — use whatever structure helps.
+
+---
+
+## Analytics Dashboard API (2026-04-03)
+
+**What was done:**
+- Created `src/models/analytics.ts` — three interfaces: `AnalyticsSummary`, `UserAnalytics`, `TrendPoint`
+- Created `src/services/analytics.service.ts` — `AnalyticsService` with constructor DI (UserRepository, OrderRepository)
+  - `getSummary()` — aggregates totalUsers, totalOrders, revenue, activeUsers (users with orders)
+  - `getUserAnalytics(userId)` — per-user orderCount, totalSpent, lastActive
+  - `getTrends(metric, startDate, endDate)` — supports 'revenue', 'orders', 'users' metrics
+- Created `tests/services/analytics.service.test.ts` — 11 tests covering all methods
+
+**Key decisions:**
+- "Active users" defined as users who have at least one order
+- `lastActive` falls back to user's `createdAt` when they have no orders
+- Trends return one TrendPoint per entity (order or user) rather than bucketed aggregations
+- No ID counter/event bus needed — this is a read-only analytics service
+
